{"data":[{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"1","text":"Neno la Bwana lililomjia Sefania mwana wa Kushi, mwana wa Gedalia, mwana wa Amaria, mwana wa Hezekia, wakati wa utawala wa Yosia mwana wa Amoni mfalme wa Yuda:"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"2","text":"Bwana asema,"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"3","text":"“Nitafagilia mbali watu na wanyama;"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"4","text":"“Nitaiadhibu Yuda"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"5","text":"wale ambao husujudu juu ya mapaa"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"6","text":"wale wanaoacha kumfuata Bwana,"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"7","text":"Nyamazeni mbele za Bwana Mwenyezi,"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"8","text":"Katika siku ya dhabihu ya Bwana"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"9","text":"Katika siku hiyo nitaadhibu wote ambao"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"10","text":"Bwana asema, “Katika siku hiyo"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"11","text":"Ombolezeni, ninyi mnaoishi katika eneo la sokoni;"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"12","text":"Wakati huo nitasaka mji wa Yerusalemu kwa taa,"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"13","text":"Utajiri wao utatekwa nyara,"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"14","text":"“Siku kubwa ya Bwana iko karibu:"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"15","text":"Siku ile ni siku ya ghadhabu,"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"16","text":"siku ya tarumbeta na mlio wa vita"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"17","text":"Nitawaletea watu dhiki,"},{"book":"Sefania","chapter":"1","verse":"18","text":"Fedha yao wala dhahabu yao"}]}